{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["小さな出来事\n\n<size=45>七　暖かさ<\/size>",1]]},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"あはははは！見たか下等生物！私の妹のカワイイ姿を！","dir":1,"bgm":"story-1","side":2,"bgmDelay":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":403040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"ね、姉ちゃん……","actor":403052,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"ふん、すでに勝負ありだと思うけど、恥を晒したいのなら特別にあんたのも見てやるわ！","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"……","actor":403051,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"……か、下等生物の分際で意外とナイスチョイスなのね……","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"しかしね！こ、これはやっぱり私の方に軍配が上がるはずだわ！","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":403040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"さあシュペー、選びなさい！","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"どっちのほうが上なのか、あなたが決めるのよ！","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"本当はさっきから頭が混乱していて、鏡の中の自分の姿をよく見れていなかった。","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"それに自分の姿を見れたとしても、どっちが上かなんて判断できるはずがない。","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"私は一体どうすれば……？","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"……","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"「そんなに深く考えなくてもいいから、素直に言っていい」って…？","actor":403050,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"最初から、私のやりたいことはわかりきっているから――","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"おい下等生物、妹に何耳打ちしたの！？抜け駆けは許さないわ！","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":403040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"シュペー、あなたの好きな方を選びなさい！信じているわ！","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"…………ふ、ふふふふ","actor":403050,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"しゅ、シュペー？急にどうしたの？","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"下等生物！妹に変なこと言って泣かしたらサメの餌にしてやるわ！","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"姉ちゃん、違うの。これ、指揮官が選んだのではなく、この間エイジャックスの言ってた服だって気づいてて……","actor":403050,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"そうよ。不安など最初から存在しなかったわ。","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"私のちっぽけな悩みは、実はこんなにたやすく解決できるの。","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"仲間がいて、友達がいて、大切にしてくれる人がいるこの母港、この艦隊は、私の心地いい居場所。","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"私、両方同じぐらい好きって言っていいの？","actor":403050,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"……はあ、そう言うだろうとちょっと思ってたわ","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"いいわ。元々この下等生物とのくだらない意地比べでしかないし、シュペーがそういうのならそれでいいわ","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"ただし！今回はシュペーに免じて許してやっただけよ！このドイッチュラントがあんたよりセンスがあることをいつか絶対に証明してやるわ！","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"指揮官、意地悪のエイジャックス、そしてドイッチュラント級の姉たち、鉄血の、艦隊の仲間――","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"守るために戦っても、それが別に守るものを受け入れないとは意味しない。","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"そう。私の願いは「ここでずっと、みんなと一緒にいる」ことなんだから……！","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"SIPEIBOJUE7","fadeOut":1.5}